    {
      "parameters": {
        "toolDescription": "Makes an HTTP request and returns the response dataRead the current feature flag by feature_id. Always call this BEFORE any mutation and AFTER any\n  mutation to verify. Input: feature_id (string). Output: { name, status, traffic_percentage,\n  depends_on, last_modified }.",
